        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-3">Dimensions &amp; Weights</h3>
        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">
          The following table lists the weights and dimensions of standard oil centrifuges. Dimensions are provided for both the bare centrifuge unit and the complete skid-mounted system, which includes the motor, piping, and control panel.
