      <!-- Specifications -->
      <div id="specifications" class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#1B3A5C] mb-4">Specifications</h2>
        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">
          The following table lists the general specifications of the oil centrifuges commonly used and listed above for capacity and weights. These specifications cover the bowl rotation speed, sludge holding capacity, motor horsepower, and startup current requirements for each model.
